    "code": "import whest as we\n\nwe.fromfunction(lambda i, j: i, (2, 2), dtype=float)\n\nwe.fromfunction(lambda i, j: j, (2, 2), dtype=float)\n\nwe.fromfunction(lambda i, j: i == j, (3, 3), dtype=int)\n\nwe.fromfunction(lambda i, j: i + j, (3, 3), dtype=int)",
